title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description:
Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
Steps to reproduce:
1. Open the report containing a table with highlights/maps.
2. Attempt to export the data from the table.

OB: No specific observed behavior statement provided.
EB: The data should be successfully exported.
SR: 
1. Open the report containing a table with highlights/maps.
2. Click on the export data button/icon.
3. Verify that the data is exported without any exceptions being thrown.
